	quest.01396882DABC0EFE.quest_desc: [
		"&bAnt Pupae&r can be found rarely by &6Brushing&r an &bAnt Mound&r."
		""
		"When &6clicked on the ground&r, they spawn baby &eTamed Ants&r, which behave like dogs! They will &afollow you, attack what you attack&r, and can have their abdomens &adyed&r."
		""
		"Beware that Adult &eTamed Ants&r will attack &aother Tamed Ants with different colored abdomens&r!"
	]
