		"&eRed Pandas&r are actually more closely related to Raccoons than &etrue Pandas&r, but that doesn't make them any less adorable!"
		""
		"They are naturally skittish creatures and will &arear up when you approach&r in an attempt to frighten you off. They can be &atamed with &bSweet Berries&r and &abred with &bBamboo&r!"
	]
