	quest.0291249FFD51DD05.quest_desc: [
		"To read a book in your &bEccentric Tome&r, &6right click&r while holding the book and &6select the book you want&r."
		""
		"To &areturn the Eccentric Tome&r to its regular form, &6hold it and left click in the air&r."
		""
		"To &aremove a book from the tome&r, you need to &6crouch and throw&r the item (default keybind is Q)."
		""
		"To &aadd a book&r, you should &6craft the book with the &bTome&r."
		""
		"&lIf you ever lose your Eccentric Tome&r, you can easily &6craft a new one&r with a &bBook&r and a &bStick&r."
	]
