	quest.03EE3579CD0561AA.quest_desc: [
		"The &cAnt Gardens&r biome is the easiest place to find &bAnthills&r. They are filled with &bRotten Leaves&r, &bCoarse Dirt&r, and spawn &bRotten Trees&r, which provide a new type of wood!"
		""
		"&bRotten Logs&r are not strong enough to craft signs and build boats, but are easier to break than regular wood. You can also obtain a new block by clicking &bRotten Planks&r with an axe: &bCracked Rotten Planks&r! These produce &ascary creaking noises&r when walked on."
	]
