	quest.047370ADE354D8DB.quest_desc: [
		"In order to read your &bBook of Shadows&r, you must first place it on a &bWooden Altar&r. In order to craft this magical pedestal, you'll need to find a &bMahogany Tree&r, located in &aJungle&r Biomes."
		""
		"The &bWooden Altar&r can also display items if you &6right click them onto its surface&r. You can also &6shift right click&r to place a block on top of them. Placing &bWooden Altars&r around your primary 2x3 &bAltar&r will &aprovide more power to it&r!"
		""
		"Also note that if you place &lHexerei&r &bcandles&r on your &bWooden Altar&r and light them, they will &afloat around as they burn&r!"
	]
