	quest.076F2A55BD9D0BCA.quest_desc: [
		"Are you an artist? Of course you are. Everyone has the ability to paint, to put pigment onto parchment. The simple act of creation is one of the most meditative pasttimes there is."
		""
		"To begin, you'll need an &bEasel&r, and a &bPalette&r. You'll also need &bCanvases&r to paint on."
	]
