	quest.07A746772D2FE875.quest_desc: [
		"&eJumping spiders&r are some of the most curious, amiable, and intelligent arthropods out there! You can &6tame them with &bDragonfly Wings&r, and as pets, they will &aprotect their owner&r!"
		""
		"If you should be so heartless as to kill one, they do &adrop &bSpider Silk&r, but as &dyou can find this resource through &bCocoons&r found throughout the world, there's little reason to hurt these sweet little beans."
