	quest.0A60EB3B10E89FE2.quest_desc: [
		"&bPacking Tape&r is an incredibly helpful item which can be used to &apackage up a storage block&r for transport. Although &dit can only be used on Sophisticated Storage&r."
		""
		"You need to &6right click the &bTape&r onto the desired item. Then you can &6break the block&r and it will retain its inventory."
	]
