	quest.0A6B50D21095E2AA.quest_desc: ["The &bFramed Key&r allows &alocking certain Framed Blocks in their current shape&r to suppress neighbor updates. This allows &aplacing blocks in configurations that would not be possible&r with the desired neighbors (i.e. placing Framed Stairs in the corner shape without keeping the necessary neighbors to force that shape)."]
