	quest.104737784582F996.quest_desc: [
		"&eHamsters&r are adorable, skittish creatures which can be found in &cPlains&r and &cMeadows&r, but most commonly in &cSunflower Fields&r. "
		""
		"Hamsters can be tamed with &bSunflower Seeds&r, a new item which drops from &bSunflowers&r. Once tamed, they can be told to sit and follow like other pets! However, beware for they are &avery territorial&r and will &aattack other &eHamsters&r that you have tamed!"
		""
		"&eHamsters&r actively collect items and put them in their cheek pouches! Once their inventory is full their cheeks will get visually larger. Adorable. Players can &6open up their Hamster's cheek pouches&r to use as storage. This is totally normal and okay."
	]
	quest.104737784582F996.quest_subtitle: "cute but territorial"
