	quest.10522CDFCA586C03.quest_desc: [
		"The &bFramed Hammer&r can be used to &aremove the &acosmetic block&r from a &framed block&r by &6right clicking&r."
		""
		"It can also be used to &acustomize the slope of a &bFramed Collapsible Block&r. &6Left click&r the corner on the face you want to change to &amove the face inward&r and &6left click the corner while sneaking&r to &amove the face outward.&r"
		""
		"The latch of the &bFramed Chest&r can be switched between three modes by &6left clicking the chest with a &bFramed Hammer&r: "
		"- Default chest latch (default state) "
		"- Camo-textured latch "
		"- No latch"
		""
		"The &bFramed Pressure Plates&r (all variants) can be switched between &awaterloggable and non-waterloggable&r by &6left-clicking them with a &bFramed Hammer&r. Their default state is non-waterloggable to match vanilla behaviour."
	]
