	quest.130C66471B8C8E27.quest_desc: [
		"From &lHexalia&r. A small, standalone brewing vessel for Hexalia's custom Herbal Brews."
		""
		"&lHow it works&r:"
		"- Place over any heat source"
		"- Throw in the required herb ingredients"
		"- Output is a Brew item - a custom potion unique to Hexalia"
		""
		"&lWhat it makes:&r All 8 Hexalia Brews: Brew of Bloodlust, Slimewalker, Spikeskin, Siphon, Daybloom, Arachnid Grace, Homestead, Hollow Silence. These are not vanilla potions - they come in Rustic Bottles and have unique effects!"
	]
