	quest.165F7D17FE6C817F.quest_desc: [
		"The &ePenguin&r as a totem is a representative of positive change and adaptability, as well as peace and harmony. The way the parents work together to raise their chick is shows excellent trust and teamwork."
		""
		"They also make great &amounts&r! You can &6tame them with raw &bCod&r or &bSalmon&r, and &6breed them with &bTropical Fish&r. Once tamed, you can equip them with an &bIce Helmet&r, and an &bIce Chestplate&r, which doubles as a &bSaddle&r!"
		""
		"When traveling over ice, they go &dextremely fast&r."
	]
