	quest.182C1C3812C31B0B.quest_desc: [
		"One of the most important tools in a witch's bag is their &bLibrary&r, in which they learn about the magical world around them, and also record their knowledge and experience as they follow their path!"
		""
		"There are two primary mods which grant you magical powers: &lHexerei&r and &lEnchanted&r. In this modpack, they are &awoven together to provide a cohesive experience&r, and as such may surprise you if you've played them before. They also both add &bguidebooks&r."
		""
		"&lHexerei's&r &bBook of Shadows&r will serve as a reference for the mechanics of that mod, and &lEnchanted's&r &bArt of Witchcraft&r - and the other volumes you'll discover as you go - will do the same for that mod. When the mechanics of the mods diverge from the guidebooks, &dthese quests will provide you the correct steps&r."
		""
		"&dNote&r: Books are important in real life, as well! &aIf you are interested in modern witchcraft&r, I recommend the following books:"
		""
		"&oWitchery&r, by Juliet Diaz"
		""
		"&oThe Witch's Path&r, by Thorn Mooney"
	]
	quest.182C1C3812C31B0B.quest_subtitle: "books are a witch's best friend"
	quest.182C1C3812C31B0B.title: "Happy Witch: Books"
