	quest.187EB99C04A3BE37.quest_desc: [
		"There are two types of eraser - &bregular&r and &bkneaded&r."
		""
		"The &bEraser&r is rather self explanatory, however - a &bKneaded Eraser&r is softer and allows you to only partially erase something, in case you want it just a bit lighter."
		""
		"Note that everything, including markers, can be erased!"
	]
