	quest.19ED6330FD3E968C.quest_desc: [
		"Normally, to get to &dThe End&r requires regular old &bEnder Eyes&r, for both seeking and filling the portal frames. However, magic has warped this world, making it more difficult to face the final dimension."
		"There are, instead, 16 other eyes (of which you need 12), which can be found in various ways. &6See the following quests&r for more information on them."
	]
