	quest.1CFE0C6B55370733.quest_desc: [
		"The &eGround Beetle&r is a delightful creature which makes a &abrave and loyal pet&r. They &dmake little chittering noises&r when you interact with them, which can be either a blessing or a curse, depending on how you feel about bugs."
		""
		"In order to tame them, you'll need &bHoneycombs&r - and you &dmay need a lot of them&r! You can &6breed two &eGround Beetles&r with &bHoney Bottles&r, at which point they will drop &bGround Larva&r, which are &aplaceable like &bTurtle Eggs&r. To incubate them, you should &6place &bTorches&6 nearby&r."
	]
	quest.1CFE0C6B55370733.quest_subtitle: "Armored Bus Beetle"
