	quest.1D27E531CF01450E.quest_desc: [
		"The &bApothecary Cauldron&r is a unique and delightful alternative to traditional &apotion brewing&r. The modern witch is handy with a potion or two, but why not challenge yourself with some &afreeform potion making&r? Not only does the &bApothecary Cauldron&r allow you to brew more powerful effects (such as &abroomless flight&r!), but it also comes with a complimentary &bApothecary Mortar&r."
		""
		"&lHow it works&r:"
		"1. Grind 2–3 ingredients in your new &bApothecary Mortar&r to create Potion Essence"
		"2. Place Potion Essence + nether wart + water in the &bApothecary Cauldron&r"
		"3. Put fire or a heat source below the cauldron"
		"4. After some time, it will outputs &bCondensed Potion&r, which can be collected in a &bCondensed Vial&r"
		""
