	quest.1EA26C716D479D14.quest_desc: [
		"The solution to your food-carrying woes is the &bLunch Box&r! Oh, of course, you could make a &bLunchbag&r instead, but we are witches and we love a sturdier option when we can find one."
		""
		"The &bLunch Box&r, and its fancier sibling, the &bGolden Lunch Box&r, will hold your food like a Shulker Box. You can then &6hold the &bLunch Box&r and &aeat it as you would do any other food&r, by &6holding right click&r. If you have a &bShield&r in your offhand, &dyou'll need to hold right click longer&r, because it's a fussier process to eat one-handed!"
		""
		"To &afill your &bLunch Box&r, you can &6shift right click&r in the air to &aopen its interface&r."
		""
		"&dA Warning&r: If you switch game modes, food in your &bLunch Box&r will be lost. But you wouldn't do that anyway... right? ;)"
	]
	quest.1EA26C716D479D14.title: "Portable Lunch"
