	quest.1EF0463BA62E3EB7.quest_desc: [
		"&eBirts&r are an unusual species which bear a passing resemblence to birds. The stalk-like antenna atop their heads allows them to communicate remotely! They live in &ahollowed-out Birch Trees&r, and each &bNest&r can contain up to 3 &eBirts&r, much like a &bBeehive&r."
		""
		"At night they &areturn to their nests&r to &alay eggs&r, which can be collected."
		""
		"&bBirt Eggs&r can be thrown like Chicken Eggs to &aspawn new Birts&r, or can be used to &6throw at enemies&r, which will cause a brief stun (Birted), which immobilizes your foe."
		""
		"You can also use them to craft a &aunique &bMusic Disc!&r"
	]
	quest.1EF0463BA62E3EB7.quest_subtitle: "next you'll meet the ernie"
