	quest.1F389C8E9F4CFB59.quest_desc: [
		"Now that you've got your artifact, the next step is to &aidentify the spell&r! &6Right clicking your artifact&r on an &bArcheology Table&r will complete this quest - though to actually identify, just &6insert your new artifact&r into the &bTable&r along with a &bBrush&r, and all the hard work is done for you!"
		""
		"Your enchantment is now identified and ready to use. If you'd like to translate its name, you can simply &6right-click your &bIdentified Artifact&r onto an &bEnchantment table&r, just like any other book!"
	]
