	quest.207C60DC8889AC0F.quest_desc: [
		"To begin with the delicious art of &aBakery&r, there are a few tools one will need. The &bCaking Station&r, the &bSimmer Pot&r, the &bCrafting Bowl&r, and, of course, an &bOven&r."
		""
		"Each of these tools will allow you to do unique things."
		""
		"The &bSimmer Pot&r allows you to create delectable &bJams&r and &bChocolate Spreads&r and such."
		""
		"The &bOven&r allows you to bake &bBreads&r, &bBuns&r, &bTarts&r, and &bmore&r!"
		""
		"The &bCaking Station&r is for the creation of &bCakes&r, &bCookies&r, and &bCupcakes&r!"
	]
	quest.207C60DC8889AC0F.quest_subtitle: "let's bake it happen"
	quest.207C60DC8889AC0F.title: "Baking Time"
