	quest.20F9C02AF5CBE665.quest_desc: [
		"FTB Teams allows you to add other players to your party, which can allow you to &ashare quest progress&r if desired, and also &aallow access to your claimed chunks&r."
		""
		"The Teams screen is accessible in the &ctop left of your inventory&r. From there, you can &acreate a party&r. You can invite others if you want to share quest progress, otherwise you can simply add other players as allies via the &bManage Allies&r screen."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/ftbmenu.png width:200 height:150 align:1}"
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/createaparty.png width:100 height:75 align:1 fit:true}"
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/manageallies.png width:200 height:150 align:1}"
		""
		"Note that &din order for Deployers and such to work in claimed chunks&r, you have to &6allow Fake Player access&r via FTB Teams. Press E and click on \"My Team\" in the top left. Then click the gear in the top right, and you'll see this menu:"
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/fakeplayers.png width:871 height:342 align:1 fit:true}"
		""
		"Set \"Allow All Fake Players\" to true."
	]
