	quest.257C8B9C7DBEEC23.quest_desc: [
		"The &bUncrafter&r is a magical salvager which can &areturn one ingredient&r from a crafted item. For example, if you put in a &bDiamond Helmet&r, you could &aretrieve one or more &bDiamonds&r from it."
		""
		"This works &aeven if the item has taken damage&r, so it could be a helpful way to salvage old gear!"
	]
