	quest.2602582F440361DB.quest_desc: [
		"The &cCell Maze&r is a structure which is filled with &aunique loot&r such as &bBee Armor&r, and will also give you something to help lead you to &aThe Queen&r. These mazes are normally located at &csea level&r."
		""
		"Entering the Maze without &bProtection of the Hive&r or having consumed the &bEssence of Bees&r (an endgame item) will give you &bWrath of the Hive&r, so be careful! Make sure to bring plenty of &asweet things&r to feed to &eBees&r and &bBrood Blocks&r!"
	]
