	quest.28ABA60CD070005E.quest_desc: [
		"To use color in your &bSketches&r, you'll need &bColored Pencils&r and/or &bMarkers&r!"
		""
		"These can be filled with all vanilla dye colors by &6right clicking the &bDye&r onto the &bEmpty Marker/Pencil&r &6in your inventory&r. Then, you can select &aany color&r from the &bColor Wheel in the bottom right&r in your Sketching interface."
	]
