	quest.293AFFA188D96753.quest_desc: [
		"Introspection is a good thing - why not &ado some Soul searching&r? Literally. Use the &bSoul Key&r to enter a tiny pocket dimension &ainside yourself&r."
		""
		"With the &bSoulKey&r in your main hand, &6hold down right click&r for a few seconds to open a portal to your innermost being."
		""
		"It's a surprisingly pleasant place! Some sunshine, grass, flowers, and even a small pond. It's an excellent place to &abegin a garden&r or &borganize your goods&r as you explore. And you can easily put down a &bCrafting Table&r and a &bFurnace&r without the need to pick them back up when it's time to move on!"
		""
		"&dWant to invite others to your &bSoulHome&r? Craft a &bBound Soul Key&r and gift it to them (perhaps via mailbox)!"
		""
		"Don't forget to check out the quest on &dLoading Chunks&r to keep your garden and furnace active while you're away!"
		""
		"🔗 Click below to view the relevant quest:"
		"[{\"text\": \"Loading Chunks\", \"clickEvent\": {\"action\": \"change_page\", \"value\": \"26D8EAD9D892805E\"}}]"
	]
	quest.293AFFA188D96753.quest_subtitle: "i found myself inside myself"
