	quest.2B1B9108FF7A3FB3.quest_desc: [
		"Now, the focus of your &asacred space&r will eventually be your &bAltar&r, but let's not get ahead of ourselves. In order to make &bAltar blocks&r, you'll need to &6collect fumes&r - namely, the &bBreath of the Goddess&r and the &bExhale of the Horned One&r."
		""
		"&aFume collection&r is done in a &bWitch's Oven&r, which is crafted with &bIron&r (to deter the fey)."
		""
		"It works similarly to a &bFurnace&r, but is limited in what it can cook, and it has additional slots which can accommodate &bClay Jars&r to &atrap the fumes&r. Take these &bSaplings&r - you may wish to plant them and obtain more before you continue - and fire these &bClay Jars&r when you get the chance."
	]
