		"&lAstikor Carts&r adds some delightful horse-drawn &bCarts&r, which are both useful and decorative. For this quest, let's focus on the latter."
		""
		"Place &bsome flowers&r above some &bdirt&r in the cart's inventory to attain this cute look! Note that you have to &6shift right click on the &bWheel&r in order to access the inventory."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/astikorflowers.png width:100 height:100 align:1 fit:true}"
	]
