	quest.2D8511D462DFF413.quest_desc: [
		"&eStonelings&r are very timid creatures! They can be found &cin caves underground&r, and will often be carrying &asomething shiny they found&r."
		""
		"Most times, they will &aimmediately flee&r the player and poof into their home dimension. However, if they are killed, they can drop the very valuable &bHeart of Diamond&r, used to make a &bPickarang&r."
		""
		"To obtain this, you'll need to &6sneak up on the &eStoneling&r."
	]
	quest.2D8511D462DFF413.title: "Meet the Stoneling"
