		"In addition to &apainting and photography&r, &asketching&r is a great way to capture the world around you! You will need a &bSketchbook&r and a &b Pencil&r to begin with, as well as an &bEraser&r to &aremove your mistakes&r."
		""
		"There are many other accessories for the &bSketchbook&r, so read on to learn more!"
		""
		"&dAll tools can be selected from the bottom of the Sketching interface, and can be put back with &6right click&r."
	]
