	quest.2E3769733A0BFF69.quest_desc: [
		"All witches ought to have a &etrusty familiar&r - traditionally, these are spirits that take the form of cats!"
		""
		"Having a &efamiliar&r will not only make you resistant to curses, but will strengthen your curse magic. More importantly, though, it's nice to have a companion. To tame a familiar, you will first need a &eCat&r. Tame it with your &bfish&r of choice, and guide it (or &6shift+right click to pick up and set down&r) into a &bRitual Circle&r."
		""
		"The book &bWitchcraft: Circle Magic&r will give you instructions on how to perform the rite."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/ritual_circle.png width:200 height:200 align:center}"
	]
	quest.2E3769733A0BFF69.quest_subtitle: "cats are also a witch's best friend"
