	quest.2F11F1501E038311.quest_desc: [
		"Never underestimate your local library! Whether you're &alooking for Enchanted books&r in &cMinecraft&r, or hoping for &awitchy resources &cirl&r, the library has what you're looking for - and it's completely free!"
		""
		"To complete this quest, you only need to find a &cLibrary structure&r. However, I task you with the additional homework of checking out some books on witchcraft irl as well!"
		""
		"Here are some of my recommendations:"
		""
		"- Everday Witchcraft, by Deborah Blake"
		"- The Green Witch, by Arin Murphy-Hiscock"
		"- Wild Witchcraft, by Rebecca Beyer"
		"- Cunningham's Encyclopedia of Magical Herbs, by Scott Cunningham"
	]
	quest.2F11F1501E038311.title: "Visit your Local Library"
