	quest.31CE923007EF1D03.quest_desc: [
		"There are a bunch of different types of &bMilk&r, which can all be made into &aunique and tasty cheeses&r."
		""
		"Although most of them come from &adifferent types of &eAnimals&r, you can also craft &bGrain Milk&r (vegan-friendly!) and &bAmethyst Milk&r. These last two types of milk are crafted using the &bRustic Cauldron&r. Grain milk is made with 2 Grains and one Wooden Water Bucket. Amethyst milk is made with Amethyst and, well, milk..."
		""
		"&eWater Buffalo&r can be found in &cRiver&r biomes."
		""
		"&eWarped Cows&r can be found in &cWarped Forest&r biomes."
	]
	quest.31CE923007EF1D03.title: "Many Milk Types!"
