	quest.327660E1DFE7C9A0.quest_desc: ["The &bBasic Pipe Upgrade&r allows you to set a &aRedstone Mode&r for the Pipe. You can set it to &aonly be active&r when receiving a signal, or to &astop when it receives a signal&r. By default, it will &aignore Redstone input&r."]
