	quest.34581095B797C667.quest_desc: [
		"Did you know that &aall true teas are the same plant&r? They're simply oxidized at different levels. Tisanes are a different story, of course, but I'll spare you the details."
		""
		"After your tea has been &aharvested at its desired color&r, it needs to be &6dried out&r - this enhances the flavor and reduces the chance of spoilage (okay, it doesn't spoil in Minecraft. Don't get sassy with me)."
		""
		"You can dry your tea leaves one of two ways: with a &bSmoker&r (faster, costs fuel) or a &bDrying Rack&r (slower, but costs only time)."
	]
	quest.34581095B797C667.title: "Drying Tea"
