	quest.3571AAEB58389A64.quest_desc: [
		"Basic chests and barrels are fine for a while, but the canny witch knows that &athe rules of space and time&r are meant to be bent a little. With a little magic, you can easily make your storage bigger - &aand smarter&r!"
		""
		"Let's begin with a simple &bBarrel&r. Place it in the world as usual, and then &6right click it with the &bBasic Tier Upgrade&r."
		""
		"Now, once you enter the inventory, you'll see some new additions."
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/sophstorage.png width:200 height:160 align:center}"
		""
		"The slot to the left &aaccepts upgrades&r which allow your storage to perform certain functions."
		""
		"The &acog wheel&r on the right gives you access to your &astorage settings&r."
	]
	quest.3571AAEB58389A64.quest_subtitle: "Let's get sophisticated"
	quest.3571AAEB58389A64.title: "Upgrading Your Storage"
