	quest.39844F8340E6A438.quest_desc: [
		"&bFramed Blocks&r are a unique item similar to &lCreate's&r &bCopycat Blocks&r. They are frameworks which can &adisplay the texture of another block&r. To do this, &6place the &bFramed Block&r and then &6right click it with another block&r."
		""
		"Framed blocks come in &a multitude of different shapes&r, many of which are not available in vanilla, such as &aslopes and corners&r. You can use this mod to elevate your builds to a new level!"
	]
	quest.39844F8340E6A438.title: "Framed Blocks"
