		"Using &aFey Magic&r, you can ensnare villagers to do your bidding~"
		""
		"By &6shift right clicking on them&r, you bewitch them into item form, which allows you to carry them around until you have need of them. While in item form, you can &aplace them into a &bTrader&r, which transforms them into a &ehomunculus&r who will then trade with you."
		""
		"Should you decide to &arelease them&r, you can &6shift right click&r on the &bTrader&r to remove the &eVillager&r, then &6right click the villager&r onto the ground."
		""
		"&bTraders&r, and other blocks from the &lEasy Villagers&r mod, will retain their inventory when broken."
	]
	quest.3A51A2B4DE09D7D7.title: "Easy Villager Trading"
