	quest.3D7070B95990779A.quest_desc: [
		"This backpack is no kid's toy - this thing is multipurpose and heavy duty! With access to a &aplethora of unique upgrades to equip&r and the ability to improve the backpack's storage by &6crafting it with increasingly expensive ingots&r, this is truly an endgame storage solution for on-the-go witches."
		""
		"You can place this backpack down/pick it up by &6shift right clicking&r it. You can &aopen it with &6b&r and &aequip it in your &bBack curio slot&r to free up inventory space."
		""
		"Caution: although you can block other players from opening your backpack while you wear it (&6check the mod's config&r!), &dthere is no way to protect against this backpack being stolen if you set it down or put it in a chest.&r"
	]
	quest.3D7070B95990779A.quest_subtitle: "its ~sophisticated~"
	quest.3D7070B95990779A.title: "Backpack For The Discerning Gentlewitch"
