	quest.3E3157BF119F4F59.quest_desc: [
		"The &bCompacting Drawer&r is super useful, as it &ataps into the fabric of reality itself&r to offer you &aa single item in multiple forms&r."
		""
		"Let me explain. Placing in 9 &bIron Ingots&r will result in the block containing - simultaneously and mutually exclusively - either 1 &bIron Block&r, 9 &bIron Ingots&r, or 81 &bIron Nuggets&r."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/compactingdrawer.png width:200 height:200 align:1}"
		""
		"If you withdraw 1 &bNugget&r, you will then have 0 &bBlocks&r, 8 &bIngots&r, and/or 80 &bNuggets&r. It simply &dsaves you the step of up or down crafting items&r."
		""
		"The &bSimple Compacting Drawer&r is similar, but works with &atwo recipes&r instead of three."
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/simplecompacting.png width:200 height:200 align:1}"
	]
	quest.3E3157BF119F4F59.quest_subtitle: "also works with vegetables!"
	quest.3E3157BF119F4F59.title: "Compact Your Iron"
