	quest.410FE13D777DE1C8.quest_desc: [
		"Now you can create your own consecrated space - your &bAltar&r. It can be placed either indoors or outdoors, although placing it outside is often a good choice due to the &apower of Nature&r being good to draw upon."
		""
		"Place &b6 Altar Blocks&r in a 2x3 configuration, and they will combine and change appearance. This is where many of your workings will take place, as it will take on and focus the energy you raise. You can &6augment this space in multiple ways&r: by placing &bFoci&r on top of the Altar, and &bobjects of power&r within a 16-block radius of it. More on this in the next quest."
		""
		"You can &aview the power of your altar by &6shift + right clicking it&r with an empty hand."
		""
	]
	quest.410FE13D777DE1C8.title: "Building an Altar"
	quest.4110A15F659422D5.quest_desc: ["The &bTrowel&r will place a random block from your hotbar when you &6right click with it&r. Perfect for easily &arandomizing your build's palette&r."]
