	quest.414A7F60BF8F090A.quest_desc: [
		"Do you struggle to draw a &aperfect circle&r? Or do you want to &adraw a straight line&r? Then these tools are for you."
		""
		"The &bDrawing Compass&r allows you to draw a circle easily by &6anchoring the point with left click&r, adjusting the radius of your circle, and then &6holding left click and spinning your cursor&r. If you experience issues with this, don't forget to &dmake sure your pencil or marker is selected&r!"
		""
		"The &bRuler&r does what it says on the tin - it...uh...rules? No, sorry, I guess it doesn't. It does help you draw a straight line, though!"
	]
