	quest.4183514EA291214A.quest_desc: [
		"&bMandrake Root&r is obtainable, surprisingly enough, from &bMandrake Plants&r! However, one must be careful when harvesting Mandrake, as they can &aget a little rowdy if agitated&r."
		""
		"To harvest just the root, &6right click&r to gather gently. However, if one were to &6left click to harvest&r, it would &aawaken the &eMandrake&r, who will &ashriek horribly&r and attempt to flee."
		""
		"However, there are &dcertain drops only available from killing the &eMandrake&r."
		""
		"To avoid its harrowing scream, &bEarmuffs&r are recommended."
	]
