	quest.41FE37817AC6ACC6.quest_desc: [
		"The &bSmudge Tool&r, simply put, helps you to &ablend out hard edges&r. However, note that the color it smudges is &dbased on the color you place it on initially&r, and if you place it over multiple colors, it will mix them. It takes some getting used to."
		""
		"The &bMagnifying Glass&r helps you to &azoom into your drawing&r to ensure perfect pixel placement! It can be used with &bany other tool&r and can be &6stowed with right click&r."
	]
	quest.41FE37817AC6ACC6.title: "Drawing Assistance 2"
