	quest.42C94ED483CD4AB8.quest_desc: [
		"The White &cSempiternal Sanctum&r grants a chance at the &bEssence of Continuity&r."
		""
		"Holding this item in offhand will make dying not kill you and instead teleport you back to your respawn point with all health restored, hunger bar filled, neutral and negative status effects removed, and fire removed. Will work in hardcore worlds too!"
		""
		"It only has 1 use before it is depleted and needs 40 minutes to recharge by being in the inventory of a player that had consumed Essence of the Bees in the past. Upon use, it will also set cooldown on all other Essence of Continuity that player has as well due to how powerful this item is."
		""
		"Upon prevention of death, the item will also give you a Written Book with details of where you were and how you almost died."
	]
