	quest.439BC18CF8CE9960.quest_desc: [
		"These teas may be unflavored, but they're certainly not flavorless! Although &bCeylon Black Tea&r, &bOolong Tea&r, and &bSencha Green Tea&r do not provide ingame effects, they do function as &adecoration blocks&r!"
		""
		"&bGreen Tea&r and &bYellow Tea&r from &lFarmer's Respite&r do grant effects, however - and you can &aextend or strengthen these effects&r by &6brewing the tea with &bMilk or Honey&r."
	]
