	quest.43CC7A6F8C1284B5.quest_desc: [
		"The &bCheese Press&r is a rudimentary machine which will help &acondense your Milk into Cheese&r. Although you can also achieve this via a &bMechanical Press&r from Create, it's always good to know the original methods of doing something!"
		""
		"Simply place your &bMilk&r and your &bRennet&r into the Press and then &6wait patiently&r (or use Time in a Bottle) for it to work its magic."
		""
		"Different &atypes of Milk&r will make unique cheeses... but more on that elsewhere!"
	]
