	quest.45FE520AC009290F.quest_desc: [
		"The Red &cSempiternal Sanctum&r grants a chance at the &bEssence of Raging&r."
		""
		"Holding this item in offhand will &ahighlight 4 nearby hostile mobs in red&r. Killing them will &agrant you &bStrength&r, and it will &ahighlight more hostile mobs&r nearby. Each highlighted kill makes your &bStrength&r effect more powerful, and maxes out at &bStrength 16&r after killing &a7 highlighted mobs&r."
		""
		"The &bStrength&r only lasts 15 seconds between kills. If time runs out, or if you kill a non-highlighted mob, the &aitem goes into 10 second cooldown&r. Making any kill after you've maxed your &bStrength&r will also set the item to cooldown."
		""
		"It has &a28 uses (highlighted kills) before it is depleted&r and needs 30 minutes to recharge. To recharge, it must &abe in the inventory of a player that has consumed &bEssence of the Bees&r. It will set cooldown on all other &bEssence of Raging&r items that player is holding as well, due to how powerful this item is."
	]
	quest.45FE520AC009290F.title: "Sempiternal Sanctum: Red"
