	quest.4655801A35B3BAB2.quest_desc: [
		"A witch's garden is a magical place, for it is here that they can commune the most deeply with nature. Placing your hands in the earth, bringing water to dry soil, feeling the breeze on your skin and the fire in your heart; it's little wonder that gardening is such a powerful feeling."
		""
		"Although any plants can bring mystic energy to a place, some are more special than others:"
		""
		"- Belladonna"
		"- Mugwort"
		"- Yellow Dock"
		"- Sage"
		"- Mandrake"
		"- Rowan"
		"- Water Artichoke"
	]
	quest.4655801A35B3BAB2.title: "Happy Witch: Garden"
