	quest.486FE1761F7E41E3.quest_desc: [
		"You did it! You've finally obtained the holy grail of foods: &bcheese&r. There are a number of incredible dishes which can be made with &ole fromage&r (pardon my French), but why not go straight to the source and make some &bFondue&r? You'll need a &bWhole Cheese Wheel&r for that, but for many recipes, you need just &aa single slice&r!"
		""
		"To &aobtain &bCheese Pieces&r, &6place down&r your Cheese Wheel and &6right click&r it with an empty hand."
	]
	quest.486FE1761F7E41E3.quest_subtitle: "that's the stuff, gromit!"
