	quest.4918B7871C3246B4.quest_desc: [
		"Collect a whole set of &bBee Armor&r to complete this quest."
		""
		"The &bStingless Bee Helmet&r, when worn, will &ahighlight all &eBees&r and &eBeehemoths&r when &6you crouch&r. You can also &6right click &eBees&r with an empty hand to &aput them on your head&r! The bee will leave your head if you &atake damage&r, &acrouch&r, &ago underwater&r, &aobtain Wrath of the Hive&r effect, or &aafter 30 seconds&r passes. &bNausea &aduration will also decrease&r twice as fast when this armor is on and &bPoison&r duration will be &aslightly decreased&r as well."
		""
		"The &bChestplate&r gives you &abrief flight&r if you &6jump after jumping&r. The &bBeenergized&r effect will improve this. It also makes you &aimmune to &bFreezing&r!"
		""
		"The &bLeggings&r allow you to resist &bSlowness&r from &lBumblezone&r blocks. You can also use them to &acollect &bPollen&r from flowers! You can use this to &6spawn a &ePollen Puff&r by &6crouching&r. Additionally, all &bSlowness&r durations will be &adecreased&r."
		""
		"These &bBoots&r can &aautomine many kinds&r of &bwood&r, &bbeehive&r, or &bhoneycomb&r blocks that you are standing on - simply &6look down and hold crouch&r."
		""
		"The boots can be enchanted with the normal boot enchantments but can also be enchanted with &bEfficiency&r, &bSilk Touch&r, and &bFortune&r. To go with Efficiency, the boots also mine faster when you have the full bee armor set on or have Beenergized status effect. These mining speed boosts &ado stack&r."
		""
		"The boots will also let you briefly hang on walls made of wood, beehive, or honeycomb blocks allowing you to wall jump or wall run!"
	]
	quest.4918B7871C3246B4.title: "The Full Set: Bee Armor, Variant 1"
