	quest.492DDC880E65C534.quest_desc: [
		"A &bStove&r is an incredibly useful tool. Thanks to your inherent magic, it is fueled at all times! You can &6place up to 6 food items&r on the grill in order to cook them. They'll pop up into items when they're ready! You can &6place an upside-down &bBasket&r above it to collect them automatically."
		""
		"The &bStove&r can also be used as a heat source for the &bCooking Pot&r, but if you do it that way, you cannot place items on the grill."
	]
	quest.492DDC880E65C534.quest_subtitle: "Steve's Stove"
	quest.492DDC880E65C534.title: "Create a Stove"
	quest.492F1C6472BC57AB.quest_subtitle: "{components:{\"ae2:facade_item\":\"colorfulazaleas:orange_flowering_azalea_leaves\"},count:1,id:\"ae2:facade\"}"
	quest.4930924C7F0BC601.quest_subtitle: "{count:1,id:\"betterend:thallasium_raw\"}"
	quest.4930ECD60EA9ED8D.quest_desc: [
		"You've obtained some &bseeds&r, congratulations! The first step of becoming a successful farmer is to have something to plant."
		""
		"As a reward, take this &bOrganic Compost&r - place it in the world and wait for it to decompose into &bRich Soil&r. Placing it near water, especially running water, will accelerate the process!"
		""
		"&bRich Soil&r will &aperiodically grant a growth boost&r to crops (when it's provided with water) and it &acannot be trampled&r. It &acan also be used to grow &bMushroom Colonies&r in complete darkness."
	]
	quest.4930ECD60EA9ED8D.quest_subtitle: "a bit seedy, perhaps"
