	quest.4B09C2508E25AD2B.quest_desc: [
		"This modpack comes with &aa lot of resourcepacks&r for you to use! Most of them should be enabled by default, but they don't always work perfectly. If you find yourself needing to do something manually - "
		""
		"We recommend enabling all of them, except for the following:"
		""
		"&7- Programmer Art"
		""
		"and that's it"
		""
		"¹ These packs have \"KatuEdit\" versions which should be enabled. They are included, disabled, in order to give proper credit to the authors. &dEdited versions of these packs&r SHOULD be enabled."
		""
		"The order in which you enable the resourcepacks &ashould not matter&r, as they are &dedited to be compatible with one another&r."
		""
		"For more information, including all resource pack credits, please visit the wiki!"
	]
	quest.4B09C2508E25AD2B.quest_subtitle: "everything in its place"
