	quest.4B26B50D268DBA07.quest_desc: [
		"It's important for us to make the distinction between simply &ofishing&r and &ostarcatching&r. You see, while both are important, one is significantly harder - and sometimes more rewarding - than the other."
		""
		"To go fishing, you'll need a &bFishing Rod&r."
		""
		"To go &ostarcatching&r (and don't ask me why it's called that - I'm a witch, not a fisherman), you'll need a &bStarcatcher's Rod&r. You can &aadd attachments&r to this rod such as new &bHooks&r and &bBobbers&r, but it cannot be otherwise upgraded, &aonly sidegraded&r, by &6using templates to change its appearance&r."
		""
		"&dSimply put - Starcatching allows you to catch unique fish&r. You go fishing for food, you go starcatching for fun."
	]
	quest.4B26B50D268DBA07.quest_subtitle: "for different, uh, bods?"
	quest.4B26B50D268DBA07.title: "Different Rods"
