	quest.4CCF9884656CBD33.quest_desc: [
		"&lFunctional Storage&r also adds &bFramed Drawers&r, which can take on &atextures from blocks&r to help &amatch your decor&r."
		""
		"To customize a &bFramed Drawer&r, you must put the Drawer into a Crafting Grid with &a2 full blocks&r - you cannot use items like &bCarpets&r or &bDragon Eggs&r (I tried)."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/frameddrawers.png width:200 height:200 align:1}"
		""
		"The &bfirst block&r will be the texture of the &aoutside&r of the Drawer."
		""
		"The &bsecond block&r will be the texture of the &ainside&r of the Drawer."
		""
		"The &bthird block&r needs to be &athe Drawer itself&r."
		""
		"Using any two full blocks ensures you can create &astorage as awesome - or as ugly - as you choose&r!"
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/frameddrawers2.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/frameddrawers3.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
