	quest.4D50F0562D23BE6D.quest_desc: [
		"&bTea&r is a small bush which can be grown in order to produce &btea leaves&r, which can be brewed into &btea&r. Let me say &btea&r some more. &bTea&r."
		""
		"You can find &bWild Tea Bushes&r in &cSwamps&r. To obtain different kinds of tea, &6allow the bush to continue growing&r until it changes color. This will allow you to gather &byellow&r and &bblack&r tea leaves!"
		""
		"&dYou cannot grow tea on &bFarmland&r, it must be planted on grass."
	]
	quest.4D50F0562D23BE6D.quest_subtitle: "the beginning of a beautiful thing"
