	quest.4DFEEDE1DAACD8B7.quest_desc: [
		"You have met the regal &eQueen Bee&r! What an honor. As it turns out, the &eQueen&r loves &ato trade&r! You can try trading random items with her, and see what you may get in return! Items can be &6dropped in front of her&r or you can &6right click her while holding them&r."
		""
		"If you don't feel like experimenting - In &lJEI&r you can see a list of &aQueen Bee Trades&r. Find the &bQueen Bee Spawn Egg&r in JEI and &6right click it&r to view all trades."
		""
		"Upon the first successful trade, you will be given &aThe Queen's Desires&r advancement line, which gives a &bRoyal Jelly Bottle&r reward for each advancement completed. After completing the entire advancement line, you get the &bEssence of the Bees&r item!"
		""
		"To track your progress, &6check your advancements&r!"
		""
		"For more information on trading, please see the next page."
		""
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"The &eBee Queen&r will sometimes pick one tradable item as a &bBonus Trade&r, and tell nearby players that she &awants that item especially, for the next 20 minutes&r. If the player trades that item with the queen, they get &a3 times the reward and xp&r!"
		""
		"They can do this up to &a24 times&r before the Queen is satisfied and the &aBonus Trade is depleted until the 20 minutes runs out&r. Then the Queen picks a new item for Bonus Trading!"
		""
		"You can &astill trade other items with the Queen&r for normal amount of rewards at any time even when the Queen is not asking for that item."
		""
		"On &acertain days of the year&r, the Bonus Trade system will turn off and the &eBee Queen&r will ask for specific items to do &aspecial trades just for those days&r! You can still do normal trades with other items during this time. These &dspecial hidden trades do not show up in &lJEI&r."
	]
