	quest.50DA655C90509B80.quest_desc: ["Ah, a familiar sight, yet somehow new! A &cWitch's Hut&r, home to one of your kin and their cat. Perhaps it would be nice to &astop in and say hello&r?"]
	quest.50DA655C90509B80.title: "Find a Better Witch Hut"
	quest.50DAF099A8888474.quest_subtitle: "{count:1,id:\"creeperoverhaul:swamp_creeper_spawn_egg\"}"
	quest.50DB7C2CED947A24.quest_subtitle: "{count:1,id:\"tide:ender_glider_bucket\"}"
	quest.50DC32C40279EF48.quest_desc: [
		"A &bSilkworm&r is the larval form of the &bSilk Moth&r, and are often found in &bSilkworm Cocoons&r growing &aon the sides of &cCottonwood&r or &cDark Oak trees&r. If you find one of these &bCocoons&r, you can either &6right click it with a torch&r to &aencourage it to hatch into a &eSilk Moth&r (this takes a few seconds) - or you can &6break the Cocoon&r to obtain the &bSilkworm&r."
		""
		"&bSilk Fiber&r can be obtained by &afeeding &bLeaves&a to &eSilkworms&r (in a crafting grid). You can then place the Fiber &6in a &bSpinning Wheel&r to produce &bSilk Thread&r, which can be used in many important recipes such as the making of &bPoppets&r and &bClothing&r."
		""
		"Note that the &bSpinning Wheel&r &dmay not appear to be doing anything&r, but it is. Just be patient!"
	]
	quest.50DC32C40279EF48.title: "Silk and Sewing"
	quest.50DCC5C0754591E4.quest_subtitle: "{components:{\"ae2:facade_item\":\"minecraft:cracked_polished_blackstone_bricks\"},count:1,id:\"ae2:facade\"}"
