	quest.50E64308D7D56C48.quest_desc: [
		"&bBellows&r are blocks that can &aspeed up furnaces&r, &aprevent fires from extinguishing&r, and even &apush entities&r."
		""
		"The rate at which the Bellows pump is determined by the strength of the &aRedstone signal&r it is receiving."
	]
