	quest.513067CD571D369E.quest_desc: ["Rumors swirl about the &bCorrupted Eye&r, of its ability to bring infinite fortune to its owner. However, the greedy king who last owned it faded into obscurity, so perhaps those rumors are just that. Legend has it that it's kept in a &dPillager Tower&r somewhere."]
