	quest.51F84C9F2CA50DA7.quest_desc: [
		"The inner world of &eBees&r is a deep one. They possess incredible intelligence, problem solving, and even have a cultural hierarchy. They the only insects which have been observed to &adance for fun&r! They represent innovation, creativity, wisdom, community, and love. &bHoney&r is often used in rituals, especially for sweetening spells."
		""
		"If you wish to delve deeper into the lives of these magical creatures, find a &bBee Nest&r and &6throw an &bEnder Pearl&r at it!"
	]
	quest.51F84C9F2CA50DA7.title: "Find a Bee's Nest"
	quest.51FAA74CE309C8E8.quest_subtitle: "{count:1,id:\"beautify:hanging_pot\"}"
