	quest.520598DFD36F43BC.quest_desc: [
		"&eRoombugs&r are flattish fellows which can be found in &cSavannahs&r and &cBadlands&r biomes."
		""
		"Roombugs are delightful, drowsy arthropods that can be &6tamed with Honeycombs&r and &6healed using Bottles of Honey&r. Tamed Roombugs can be &aridden by the player&r or commanded to sit down, during which they may loudly doze off to sleep."
		""
		"Sleeping roombugs can be &amounted by entities&r, and can then move around with mounted entities on their back. &6Shift + Right Click&r allows the player to &aforcefully dismount entities&r that are riding a &eroombug&r. This introduces a quick, convenient way to relocate entities. "
	]
	quest.520598DFD36F43BC.title: "Meet the Roombug"
