	quest.52BC8196E858B238.quest_desc: [
		"Gain this advancement by taming and befriending an animal!"
		""
		"Using the &bCage&r reward from this quest, you can right click to place an entity in your inventory so you can easily move them large distances. Simply &6right click the &bCage&r on the animal, and then &6right click it on a block&r to place the animal down again."
		""
		"You can also &6shift right click&r to place the &bCage&r as a block to display your new pal. Putting your friends in cages is &ototally normal&r."
	]
	quest.52BC8196E858B238.quest_subtitle: "IDK, my BFF Cow?"
