	quest.54F9B41F96399DE6.quest_desc: [
		"As you might know, the &bEnchanting Table&r is a device which is used to &aimbue your gear with magic&r, and requires the power of &bKnowledge&r, both in &bBookshelf&r and &bExperience&r form."
		""
		"Unlike in vanilla, however, this &bEnchanting Table&r has a chance to &aapply Curses&r to your gear in addition to beneficial enchantments. In order to navigate this new challenge, it's encouraged to check out options such as &6disenchantment&r."
		""
		"&bDisenchantment&r can be pursued either through &lCognition's&r &bPrecision Dispeller&r, or &lTombstone's&r &bBook of Disenchantment&r."
	]
	quest.54F9B41F96399DE6.title: "Challenging Enchanting"
