	quest.561E0AC36A0C1DB4.quest_desc: ["To use the &bFondue Pot&r, you must first place it atop a &bStove&r, and then &6right click it with a &bCheese Wheel&r to fill it. Once filled, take some &bBread&r and &6dip it in&r - you can get up to &a3 servings&r of a highly nutritious food this way!"]
	quest.561E0AC36A0C1DB4.quest_subtitle: "well that's a 'fon' how 'due' you do"
