	quest.56497A1094C28B5F.quest_desc: [
		"The &eAngler Fish&r is a creature which spawns &anear the bottom&r of &cDeep Oceans&r. You will be able to find them by their &asignature glow&r."
		""
		"They can be &acaptured in a bucket&r, and it may be very beneficial to have one - &6feed one something shiny&r (&bgems, gold, glowing things&r) to be granted &a5 minutes of &bNight Vision&r!"
		""
		"Keep in mind that &eAngler fish&r cannot withstand the pressure of being on land and will promptly deflate when exposed to air."
	]
