	quest.5688211768F55F90.quest_desc: [
		"Practicing witchcraft is just one aspect of actually being a witch, but it is arguably the most important - and the most fun!"
		""
		"A happy witch has three things: a &agarden&r, a &asacred space&r, and &blots of books&r. And probably also &bcoffee&r. And &ecats&r! Okay, so a happy witch has lots of things. But let's begin with the &bBooks&r."
	]
