	quest.573269BC454A499D.quest_desc: [
		"You &aprint your photographs&r using the &bLightroom&r. Here you can &aview your developed negatives&r in detail, as well."
		""
		"&bBlack and White Film&r requires &bPaper&r and &bBlack Dye&r. Printing in &acolor&r additionally requires &bCyan&r, &bMagenta&r, and &bYellow Dyes&r."
		""
		"Once you have &6chosen your photo with left click&r, you can then &6click the checkmark&r to begin printing. And ta-da! Photographs!"
	]
