	quest.57CEB5677AF42CCB.quest_desc: [
		"&bBrooms&r are incredibly useful to have. Not only do they make a stylish decoration, but you can use them to &asweep up messes&r such as &bSalt&r, &bAsh&r, and more! Pretty cool, right?"
		""
		"Okay, yeah, fine, you can also use them to fly. But it's not easy! Taking a mundane &bBroom&r and turning it into a &bflying Broom&r requires some power, some components, and some time!"
		""
		"Make yourself some &bFlying Ointment&r, and we can move on to the next step."
	]
