	quest.598D07A8C3ED765A.quest_desc: [
		"Otters! Otters spawn in rivers and will open clams that you give them for the occasional chance at pearls. Use these to craft a pearl necklace. Stronger versions of pearl necklaces increase swim speed, lessen drowned detection and at third tier, lessens guardian detection. "
		""
		"Sea bunny! Sea bunnies can have bottles used on them."
		"It gives bottles of slime. Those can make blocks. Bucketable."
		""
		"Dumbo Octopus! Bucketable. Gives drowning players a bubble helmet if nearby. "
		""
		"Leaf insect! Dances to music. Join the parrots. "
		""
		"Koi fish! Bucketable. Groups give the player luck. "
	]
