	quest.5C5768D4346FD3FE.quest_desc: [
		"The &bVendor&r is a block which allows players to &atrade items for currency&r in multiplayer."
		""
		"You can &6right click the vendor&r to buy the contents, as long as you have either &bexact change&r or a &bCard&r in your inventory. Look at the tooltip to determine &awhat you're buying and how much it costs&r."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/numibuy.png width:100 height:90 align:1 fit:true}"
		""
		"See the next page to view how to &aset up your &bVendor&r to buy or sell!"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/numivendor.png width:100 height:80 align:1 fit:true}"
		""
		"&eA&r: These sections allow you to determine the price of the item you're selling. For example, something could cost 1 &bCrown&r and 2 &bSpurs&r."
		""
		"&bB&r: This section is where your profits will go if you don't have a card inserted to transfer your profits directly to your bank."
		""
		"&cC&r: This box determines what you're selling. You can place up to a stack of items in this slot. This slot will &adisplay the item&r, but it will show as &dout of stock if slot E isn't filled&r. If you wish to sell a bundle of items, you can put it inside a &bShulker Box&r. If you use a &bSack&r or similar, the &dcontents will not be displayed to your customers&r."
		""
		"&9D&r: You can place a &blinked Card&r in this slot to have all profits deposit straight into your &bBank Account&r."
		""
		"&dE&r: This section is where you place your &ainventory of items&r to sell."
		""
		"&aF&r: This section determines whether you are &abuying or selling&r. "
	]
	quest.5C5768D4346FD3FE.title: "Multiplayer Bartering"
