	quest.5C8A806847060D9D.quest_desc: [
		"The &bShiny Beetle&r is very similar to the &bGround Beetle&r, except it &acan fly&r! Like its terrestrial sibling, you can &6tame the &eShiny Beetle&r with &bHoneycomb&r, and &6breed it with &bHoney Bottles&r."
		""
		"Once bred, they will &adrop a &bFlying Beetle Larva&r, which you can &6place down like a &bTurtle Egg&r, and &aincubate with heat sources&r such as &bTorches&r."
	]
