	quest.5D1EFA0ECBE9891C.quest_desc: [
		"The &bEye of Ender&r was once used to find the &cStrongholds&r of old. However, these no longer function the way they once did."
		""
		"To locate the &cStronghold&r, the modern witch uses an &bExplorer's Compass&r! You can also throw &bEyes&r from &lEnd Remastered&r, but as they are harder to come by, this is not advised."
	]
