	quest.5D37E0A2F297C49E.quest_desc: [
		"Ah, here we are! Combine the &bChocolate Spread&r and &bCake Dough&r you made in a &bBaking Station&r."
		""
		"An indulgent treat, this &bChocolate Cake&r should keep you sated for a while!"
		""
		"Or, if you're so inclined, you could &aprogress to the next quest&r and &afind a way to &6display it&r! Actually, here, take these two &bCake Slices&r. That way you can &aeat your cake, and have it, too&r."
		""
		"Yes, I know that's now how the phrase goes. But if you think about it, it really makes more sense this way."
	]
