	quest.5D56599E8A52F61B.quest_desc: [
		"There are a number of different &bDrawer Upgrades&r. There are the &bMetal Upgrades&r, which &aincrease drawer capacity&r. There is the all-important &bVoid Upgrade&r, which prevents the server from lagging by &avoiding excess items&r. And there are the utility upgrades:"
		""
		"- &bPulling Upgrade&r: It pulls items from an adjacent inventory"
		""
		"- &bPushing Upgrade&r: It pushes items to an adjacent inventory"
		""
		"- &bCollecting Upgrade&r: It collects items on the ground directly in front of it"
		""
		"- &bRedstone Upgrade&r: Gives off a redstone signal based on how full the drawer is. Can be configured to read different slots in multi-slot drawers"
