	quest.5FC2335FA7C31389.quest_desc: [
		"The &lBeautify&r &bLattices&r can hold flowers! You can use"
		""
		"- &bSunflowers&r"
		"- &bPeonies&r"
		"- &bRose Bushes&r"
		"- &bLilac&r"
		"- &bGlow Lichen&r"
		"- &bVines&r"
		"- &bWeeping Vines&r"
		"- &bTwisting Vines&r"
		""
		"Be aware that the &lSpawn&r mod &dreplaces vanilla &bSunflowers&r, which means they need to &abe converted to vanilla in your crafting grid&r before you can use them."
	]
