	quest.612B4F05F1E3636D.quest_desc: [
		"Once you have pigments on your &bPalette&r, you can &6mix them together&r on the &aright side of your Palette&r."
		""
		"Use the &aWater&r on your Palette to erase a mixed color. Use the &ablending options&r on the right of the &bCanvas&r to blend your colors together. Change your &abrush size&r there, too! If you make a mistake while painting, you can &6ctrl+z to undo&r, or &6right click to erase&r."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/joyofpainting.png width:100 height:80 align:1 fit:true}"
		""
		"You can toggle tooltips using the button in the &atop right&r (not pictured)."
		""
		"At any time, you can &6shift left click&r the &bEasel&r to take your painting down. You can &6hang the painting by right clicking it&r on a wall. You can remove it and edit it &aas long as you haven't signed it yet&r."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/joyofpaintingsign.png width:100 height:90 align:1 fit:true}"
		""
		"Once you've signed it, it can no longer be edited, but it will be named what you titled it, and will show your name as the artist! Nice work!"
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/joyofpaintingdone.png width:100 height:100 align:1 fit:true}"
	]
	quest.612B4F05F1E3636D.title: "Begin a Painting"
