	quest.6138C299ED7CE80C.quest_desc: [
		"The &bHammock&r is an item which allows you to &aprogress the time to night&r by taking a &anice, relaxing nap&r during the day."
		""
		"You'll need to first make sure you have exactly &dfour blocks of space&r for the &bHammock&r. Place the &bRope and Nail&r on two blocks, four blocks apart. Then you can &6right click the &bHammock Cloth&r into place."
	]
