	quest.62D95F91881F228C.quest_desc: [
		"There are a number of &ajar types&r in this modpack."
		""
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/jartypes.png width:150 height:100 align:1}"
		""
		"The one from &lSupplementaries&r can hold up to &athree buckets of liquid&r and can also hold &bCookies&r, or even &bBucketed Fish&r! You can &aeat edibles&r from the jar by &6right clicking&r."
		""
		"You can also capture small mobs such as &eSlimes&r and &eBees&r. You can &aplace the jar by crouching and right clicking&r it. If you &6simply right click&r, you will release the creature."
		""
		"The &bJar&r from &lBakery&r can hold &bJams&r."
		""
		"And finally, the &bGlass Jar&r from &lMystic's Biomes&r is capable of capturing &eCaterpillars&r and &eButterflies&r! &dThis jar cannot be placed&r."
		""
		"The &bJar&r from &lHearth and Home&r can be used to &acraft jams&r, but can also be &aplaced down&r, fitting up to &a4 jars in one block&r!"
	]
	quest.62D95F91881F228C.quest_subtitle: "jar jar is the heart of it"
	quest.62D95F91881F228C.title: "Differentiating Jars"
