	quest.635FE9332FFCE4A7.quest_desc: [
		"The &bEssence of the Bees&r is acquired by &acompleting the &bQueen's Desire&r advancement line, which is unlocked after &atrading with her&r for the first time."
		""
		"It is a consumable item which &agives you pleasant pheremones&r, soothing nearby &eBees&r. You gain the following &dpermanent bonuses&r:"
		""
		"- Actions which previously activated &bWrath of the Hive&r will no longer do so."
		"- Entering the &cThrone Pillar&r will no longer grant &bMining Fatigue&r."
		"- Entering &bHoney Fluid&r will grant Regenerative effect."
		"- Entering &bRoyal Jelly Fluid&r will grant a short lived Beenergized effect and stronger Regenerative effect."
		"- &bBeehive/Bee Nests&r can be mined, &bhoney&r taken by bottle, or sheared for &bhoneycombs&r without angering the bees. No campfire needed!"
		"- &eHoney Slime&r will not get angry at you for taking its honey."
		"- Standing on &bLuminescent Wax&r will start granting beneficial effects instead of negative ones."
		"- Allows usage of endgame Bumblezone &bEssence&r items. Their abilities are now usable by the player."
		""
		"Additionally, new &bHoney Compasses&r pointing towards &cSempiternal Sanctums&r will begin showing up in &cBumblezone Loot&r."
	]
