	quest.644439D23D454629.quest_desc: [
		"There are few things more enjoyable than a delicious hot beverage. As with all kitchen witchery, making tea and coffee can be an important daily ritual, and the same goes for doing so in game. To begin, you'll need a &bKettle&r."
		""
		"The &bKettle&r must be &6placed on a heat source&r in order to brew tea. You can use a &bcampfire&r, &bmagma block&r, or other source of warmth."
		""
		"Use a &bwater bucket&r or 3 &bwater bottles&r to fill the &bkettle&r with water by &6right clicking them&r on the block. Then, &6right click&r and place your brewing ingredients inside!"
	]
	quest.644439D23D454629.quest_subtitle: "Don't let it call your Cooking Pot black."
	quest.644439D23D454629.title: "Obtain a Kettle"
