	quest.649CD989B90CED8A.quest_desc: [
		"The &cSempiternal Sanctums&r are endgame structures which should not be visited until one has consumed the &bEssence of Bees&r. Visiting without bee pheremones will result in &aMining Fatigue&r, &aincreased damage from &eSentries&r, and &athe inability to trigger &bSanctum Events&r."
		""
		"At the top of the structure is &aa garden full of Rootmins on patrol&r. Flowers matching the structure's color will be spawned. Upon entering the hole in the center, the player can navigate a &cdeadly maze&r full of &eSentry Watchers&r and collect great loot!"
		""
		"But if the player manages to find their way into the center heart of the structure, they will find a room with a colorful &bEssence Block&r in the center, which matches the color of the structure. &6Touching this Essence Block&r will trigger an &aarena event&r! Each sanctum has a different event and a different endgame reward item for beating said event. The events can be very difficult, so come prepared! Once an event is finished, it &acan be repeated&r by &6clicking the &bEssence Block&r again."
		""
		"The powerful items you can obtain are as follows:"
		""
		"&bEssence of Raging&r (red)"
		""
		"&bEssence of Radiance&r (yellow)"
		""
		"&bEssence of Life&r (green)"
		""
		"&bEssence of Calming&r (blue)"
		""
		"&bEssence of Knowing&r (purple)"
		""
		"&bEssence of Continuity&r (white)"
	]
	quest.649CD989B90CED8A.title: "Find a Sempiternal Sanctum"
