	quest.694D0C4F0DCF078C.quest_desc: [
		"Your Sophisticated &bBarrels&r and &bChests are capable of &aholding more than a stack per slot&r, if you use the &bStack Upgrades&r on them. The higher the tier, the more stacks each slot can hold."
		""
		"You can also &ause more than one Stack Upgrade&r, and they will add &amultiplicatively&r!"
		""
		"So if you use a &bTier 1&r and a &bTier 2&r, you will hold 2 stacks by 4 stacks, meaning 8 stacks, or &d512 items per slot&r."
	]
