	quest.6AF9BE2037D01B2A.quest_desc: [
		"Your &bAltar&r can be &aupgraded with various foci and sources of power&r. A &bFocus&r is &dplaced on top of the altar&r, and &bsources of power&r should be placed around it, &dwithin 16 blocks&r."
		""
		"Examples of &bFoci&r are:"
		"- Light sources such as &btorches&r, &bcandles&r, and &bcandelabras&r"
		"- &bSkulls&r or &bplayer heads&r"
		"- &bChalices&r or &bgoblets&r"
		""
		"Different options may provide more or less power, so &ado some experimenting&r to see what works the best for you."
		""
		"&bSources of power&r are items which, when surrounding your &bAltar&r, will lend &amagical energy to it&r. Here are some examples:"
		"- &bWooden Altars&r"
		"- &bBudding or growing Crystals&r"
		"- &bHerb Jars&r"
		"- &bWitchy plants and trees&r"
		""
		"Also, be sure to include your other witchy tools such as the &bMixing Cauldron&r, &bKettle&r, &bMortar \\& Pestle&r, and more! If you use it in your practice, it's good to have it near your &bAltar&r."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/altarsetup.png width:300 height:250 align:center}"
	]
