	quest.6BADAB3BD0E50555.quest_desc: [
		"The Yellow &cSempiternal Sanctum&r grants a chance at the &bEssence of Radiance&r."
		""
		"This item is active when &athe player is in a place visible to the sun&r. While held in the offhand, it provides &bRegeneration&r, &bSaturation&r, &bSpeed&r, &bHaste 2&r, and &bDamage Resistance 2&r. It also &aslowly repairs armor over time&r."
		""
		"It has &a4800 uses before it is depleted&r and needs 10 minutes to recharge. It will only recharge in the inventory of someone who has &aconsumed &bEssence of the Bees&r."
	]
	quest.6BADAB3BD0E50555.title: "Sempiternal Sanctum: Yellow"
