	quest.6BE389D26249D046.quest_desc: [
		"In order to perform &bCircle Magic&r, you'll need different &bChalks&r, in addition to the ritual &bFoci&r, and of course, a nearby &bAltar&r with &aenough Power&r."
		""
		"Using this type of magic, you can do everything from &aforging a Mixing Cauldron&r to &amaking a flying broom&r to &ataming a Familiar&r!"
		""
		"In addition to the chalk circles on the outside, every rite requires a &brune of Golden Chalk&r in the center, which should be &6right clicked with the &bGolden Chalk&r after the reagents are placed. This will &aactivate the ritual&r."
		""
		"A successful ritual will consume your reagents one by one and then provide the desired output. If at the end, your reagents are spat back out, then &dthe ritual has failed&r. Double check your &bingredients&r and that your &bAltar&r is &aclose enough and has enough Power&r."
