	quest.6C25F07248AC8170.quest_desc: [
		"Although the two are not commonly thought of together, &bwitchcraft&r and &barchaeology&r are actually well interwoven. Both revere the bones of our ancestors, both emphasize a respect for the natural world, and both are deeply interested in &aancient ways&r."
		""
		"Anthropology and archaeology are excellent fields of study for witches who want to uncover and deciper ancient mysteries. So why not get yourself started with a &bBrush&r?"
	]
	quest.6C25F07248AC8170.title: "Anthropology 101"
