	quest.6C3861D0B545A88F.quest_desc: [
		"&bSugar Water&r is a substance commonly found in the &cSugar Water Floor&r biome of the &bBumblezone&r. You can &6bottle it&r and then use those bottles to &6feed Bees&r or &bHoneycomb Brood Blocks&r. When doing the latter, it &afeeds the growing pupa&r and will eventually &aspawn a baby &eBee&r."
		""
		"When doing the former, you can possibly get the &aProtection of the Hive&r effect!"
	]
	quest.6C3861D0B545A88F.title: "Obtain Sugar Water"
