	quest.6E447D4984BAA0EB.quest_desc: [
		"The &bStorage Controller&r is a block which &amagically communes with the surrounding drawers&r. This will allow you to &atransfer items into or out of your network&r through a single block, instead of needing to hook up every single inventory."
		""
		"It requires a &bLinking Tool&r in order to communicate with the surrounding &bDrawers&r. &6Hold the Linking Tool&r to view the radius the &bController&r can reach. Then, simply &6right click the &bTool&6 onto the &bController&r to assign it. Then &6right click your drawers&r to connect them!"
	]
	quest.6E447D4984BAA0EB.quest_subtitle: "one block to rule them all!"
