	quest.6EFFB8ED37DC8A47.quest_desc: [
		"The &lSpice Of Life&r is a mod which rewards you for eating a &adiverse diet of well-balanced foods&r. While you can survive on nothing but &bBread&r and &bGolden Carrots&r, you'll find that you thrive if you make and eat more rewarding foods - which this pack offers a LOT of."
		""
		"You can view the benefits in your &bFood Book&r in your &bEccentric Tome&r."
		""
		"When you hover over a piece of food, you'll be able to see its &adiversity value&r, and the &aamount of diversity it will add to your score&r (in parentheses). If you have a high diversity score and eat something of low diversity, it will &alower your average diversity&r and the number will show in red instead of green."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/spiceoflife1.png width:180 height:180 align:1}"
		""
		"Additionally, &aeating the same food repeatedly&r will not improve your diversity score. But wait, you say, I can't go carrying around that much food! I'm a witch, not a pack mule! To this I reply: go to the next quest."
	]
	quest.6EFFB8ED37DC8A47.quest_subtitle: "(psst, it's variety)"
	quest.6EFFB8ED37DC8A47.title: "The Spice of Life"
