	quest.7210927B460B6B0F.quest_desc: [
		"One might not necessarily assume that a &cSwamp&r is the most pleasant place to form a village - but you'd be wrong!"
		""
		"For one thing, you get unlimited access to cute &eFrogs&r, delightfully squishy &bMud&r, and plenty of water for your crops."
		""
		"Once you &asee one for yourself&r, you'll understand the charm."
	]
