	quest.7232C9D413054886.quest_desc: ["Need to get somewhere in a hurry? Why not try &aslinging&r? The &bSlime Sling&r, when &6pointed at the ground and drawn&r, will shoot the player in the opposite direction upon release. You can achieve &aquite a bit of air time&r this way! And the &bSlime Boots&r make it so you...you know...&adon't die from fall damage&r. A winning combination!"]
