	quest.724475964CA8B68D.quest_desc: [
		"These upgrades allow your backpack to operate outside the confines of its leather!"
		""
		"- &bPickup Upgrade&r will reroute any items you pick up to enter your backpack instead of your inventory. "
		"- &bMagnet Upgrade&r will draw items to your backpack from a distance! "
		"- &bJukebox Upgrade&r will allow you to be that one hiker who always brings their bluetooth speaker with them to bless the entire trail with the soothing tunes of Nicki Minaj."
		""
		"To get the most of these upgrades, we suggest &6checking out the settings tab&r for each one. "
		""
		"Your settings will be saved for each upgrade &aeven if you remove it.&r"
	]
