	quest.72CE099C5784339A.quest_desc: [
		"The &bSpyglass&r (or &bGlasses&r) is quite an underrated tool. To begin with, it allows you to &aview distant things&r without having to leg it all the way over yonder. But that's just the beginning!"
		""
		"Perhaps more importantly, they allow you to &aresearch the world around you&r. Encounters with even the most mundane creatures will &agrant you experience&r and &aunlock &lField Guide&r &aentries&r."
		""
		"The &bGlasses&r have the added bonus of being &awearable and usable with a hotkey&r."
	]
