	quest.775A1B6549572BEB.quest_desc: [
		"The &bVoid Upgrade&r is an item which will &aremove unwanted items from your storage&r. It will, quite simply, delete them, ensuring that your storage is both well-organized and your server un-crashed. &dIt is especially important to use this upgrade for farms&r!"
		""
		"You can configure it to &adelete only overflow items&r or, if you prefer, &adelete all items of specific type&r."
		""
		"{image:enchanted_wilds:textures/questimages/voidoverflow.png width:100 height:25 align:1 fit:true}"
		""
		"The &bAdvanced Void Upgrade&r is capable of sorting by NBT and Damage levels."
	]
