		"The &bArthana&r, sometimes called an &bAthame&r, is a ritual dagger which causes &acertain unique drops&r to be obtained from various creatures, such as &bBat's Wool&r and &bCreeper Hearts&r."
		""
		"It can also be used to harvest certain items from plants, such as &bTongue of Dog&r from &bWolfsbane Flowers&r."
	]
