	quest.79B6B78157E7D32C.quest_desc: ["&bThe Moonworm Queen&r is an...item...that is filled with Moonworms. When you &6right click her&r, they will be dispensed - either directly onto a surface, or shot like an arrow. The moonworms serve no purpose other than &aas a light source&r. You can replenish the Queen by crafting her with &bTorchberries&r, and get...even more worms. Yay."]
