	quest.7B3D377F253BFF4A.quest_desc: [
		"&bHerbal Teas&r are commonly used in witchcraft as &atreatments to various ailments&r."
		""
		"&bLavender Tea&r, for example, is good for anxiety and can also call &alove into your life&r. It will boost your &bFortune&r for a while."
		""
		"&bYerba Mate&r is a strongly stimulating tea, making it &agood for fatigue&r or other such maladies. It does not grant ingame effects."
		""
		"&bDandelion Tea&r is made by steeping Dandelion root, and is used as a replacement for coffee. It will also grant you the &bComforting&r effect, which &akeeps you healing regardless of hunger&r."
		""
		"&bRose Hip Tea&r is a delicious floral which can aid in &aglamour spells, good luck, and prosperity&r! and Additionally, it will grant you a small amount of &bRegeneration&r!"
	]
	quest.7B3D377F253BFF4A.title: "Herbal Teas"
