		"These upgrades will help you take your workshop with you. Each one does what it says on the tin... &bcrafting tables&r, &banvils&r, &bstonecutters&r... who needs a base? You can live the life of a true adventurer."
		""
		"To get the most of these upgrades, we suggest &6checking out the settings tab&r for each one. "
		""
		"Your settings will be saved for each upgrade &aeven if you remove it.&r"
	]
