		"To begin with, you'll need a &bFelting Needle&r, and some &bWool&r. &6Hold the &bWool&6in your off hand and &6hold the &bNeedle&r in your main hand, then &6hold right click&r to &lSTAB THAT WOOL LIKE IT BETRAYE&r - eh, uh, ahaha. Sorry. Anyway."
		""
		"Not all wools will work with this process, but why not &atry several different kinds&r and see what you can come up with?"
	]
