	quest.7F52A3C01776886D.quest_desc: [
		"When you die, you &alose most of your experience levels&r - but it doesn't have to be this way! We are magic, after all. "
		""
		"There are many methods through which you can &abank your experience&r to use for later. For example, your &bBackpack&r has an upgrade which allows you to &astore liquid exp&r."
		""
		"There is also the &bHero's Medallion&r, which you can &6right click or shift right click&r to deposit/retrieve experience."
	]
