	quest.7FE2C3E2F1129E9D.quest_desc: [
		"&eAnts&r are industrious little creatures that make their homes in &bAnthills&r. They can be found in &cSavannahs&r, &cPlains&r, and &cForests&r."
		""
		"They are &aneutral&r, but if you anger one, the &awhole hive will fight back&r!"
		""
		"&eAnts&r work like &eBees&r, and can live in &bAnthills&r (spawn naturally) or &bAnt Farms&r (craftable). They also &acollect resources from Dead Bushes and Tall Grass&r and bring them back to their home."
		""
		"&bAnthills&r that have the resource level of three &arandomly turn blocks in a 3x3 radius below them into rotten versions of themselves&r, consuming all three of the resource levels. "
		""
		"&bLogs&r become &bRotten Logs&r and &bDirt-like blocks&r become &bAnt Mounds&r. "
	]
